Imperium_root/
│
├── Imperium.py/  - Project main source code
├── Imperium.kv/  - kivy file for global kivy settings for the project
├── requirements  - technical requirements to run the project

├── assets/
    ├── audio/    - all the audio files in the project (in mp3 format)
    ├── images/   - all the sources for images in the project
    ├── images/   - all the video files in the project (in mp4 format)

├── src/ (further explanation in the files themselves)
    ├── __init_.py/         - project init
    ├── A_star.py/          - A* Algorithm with Node class
    ├── constants.py/       - project constants
    ├── Empire.py/          - Empire class
    ├── Hexes.py            - Hexes file with Hex classes
    ├── Info_Button.py/     - Info Button class
    ├── Next_Turn_Button.py/- Next-Turn Button class
    ├── Screens.py/         - Screens file with Screen classes
    ├── Units.py/           - Units file with Unit classes


├── README        - project description
├── LICENSE       - Standard MIT license provided by Github
